      "et_speech_frac": 0.66,
      "kiel_max_innovation": 0.62,
      "semantic_score": 0.192,
      "formant_ratio": 0.614,
      "token_count": 16,
      "speaker_turn": false,
      "text": " Let's talk about the post-mortem, part one, blameless."
    },
    {
      "t0_ms": 39280,
      "t1_ms": 44800,
      "confidence": 0.9246,
      "quality": 0.9246,
      "hcp_quality": 1.0000,
      "hallucination_flags": 0,
      "hcp_flagged_tokens": 6,
      "et_rms": 0.0910,
      "et_speech_frac": 0.85,
      "kiel_max_innovation": 0.40,
      "semantic_score": 0.206,
      "formant_ratio": 0.649,
      "token_count": 21,
      "speaker_turn": false,
      "text": " A post-mortem is basically a specialized retrospective, where you look back at what happened and what you"
    },
    {
      "t0_ms": 44800,
      "t1_ms": 50160,
      "confidence": 0.9490,
      "quality": 0.9490,
      "hcp_quality": 1.0000,
      "hallucination_flags": 0,
      "hcp_flagged_tokens": 5,
      "et_rms": 0.0904,
      "et_speech_frac": 0.86,
      "kiel_max_innovation": 0.68,
      "semantic_score": 0.290,
      "formant_ratio": 0.627,
      "token_count": 25,
      "speaker_turn": false,
      "text": " can learn from it. But instead of looking back at a sprint from a retrospective, you're now looking back at a"
    },
    {
      "t0_ms": 50160,
      "t1_ms": 56320,
      "confidence": 0.8530,
      "quality": 0.8530,
      "hcp_quality": 1.0000,
      "hallucination_flags": 16,
      "hcp_flagged_tokens": 8,
      "et_rms": 0.0917,
