      "et_speech_frac": 0.79,
      "kiel_max_innovation": 0.57,
      "semantic_score": 0.289,
      "formant_ratio": 0.646,
      "token_count": 23,
      "speaker_turn": false,
      "text": " But the thing with a post-mortem and a retrospective is that it can easily turn into a blame game."
    },
    {
      "t0_ms": 65760,
      "t1_ms": 71600,
      "confidence": 0.8807,
      "quality": 0.8807,
      "hcp_quality": 1.0000,
      "hallucination_flags": 0,
      "hcp_flagged_tokens": 5,
      "et_rms": 0.1078,
      "et_speech_frac": 0.86,
      "kiel_max_innovation": 0.51,
      "semantic_score": 0.357,
      "formant_ratio": 0.548,
      "token_count": 22,
      "speaker_turn": false,
      "text": " And the thing with blame is that it decreases the psychological safety. And when you are blaming, when you"
    },
    {
      "t0_ms": 71600,
      "t1_ms": 77760,
      "confidence": 0.9630,
      "quality": 0.9630,
      "hcp_quality": 1.0000,
      "hallucination_flags": 0,
      "hcp_flagged_tokens": 4,
      "et_rms": 0.1003,
      "et_speech_frac": 0.76,
      "kiel_max_innovation": 0.54,
      "semantic_score": 0.209,
      "formant_ratio": 0.612,
      "token_count": 20,
      "speaker_turn": false,
      "text": " have a low psychological safety, you are preventing your group from learning. Blame prevents people from"
    },
    {
      "t0_ms": 77760,
      "t1_ms": 84320,
      "confidence": 0.9095,
      "quality": 0.9095,
      "hcp_quality": 1.0000,
      "hallucination_flags": 0,
      "hcp_flagged_tokens": 6,
      "et_rms": 0.0910,
      "et_speech_frac": 0.72,
      "kiel_max_innovation": 0.61,
      "semantic_score": 0.130,
      "formant_ratio": 0.554,
      "token_count": 23,
      "speaker_turn": false,
      "text": " speaking up with concerns, from pointing out each other's mistakes and blind spots. It creates a culture of fear"
    },
    {
      "t0_ms": 84320,
      "t1_ms": 90720,
      "confidence": 0.9406,
      "quality": 0.9406,
      "hcp_quality": 1.0000,
      "hallucination_flags": 0,
      "hcp_flagged_tokens": 4,
      "et_rms": 0.0962,
